{"tid":2494960,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"泰IG女神Davika破千三萬followers 沙灘寫真激似美人魚","createTime":"2021-04-19T01:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-19T03:32:00.000Z","uid":16659,"like":27,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"3d79bdf607bf0675e93a674109fe119ef2c8a283","tid":2494960,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T01:50:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KHHlTzpXqn1d0rUmhGXUXbZVd18=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MAOD3AEQVBHONFULN7GD4A2ETI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKHHlTzpXqn1d0rUmhGXUXbZVd18%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMAOD3AEQVBHONFULN7GD4A2ETI.jpg&h=904f3760&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國女神Davika Hoorne走紅當地影視圈，與影星男友奇塔維達納韋（Ter）亦感情穩定，被睇好隨時拉埋天窗，可謂事業愛情兩得意。<br />\n<br />\nDavika Hoorne下月將迎接其29歲生日，雖然泰國人最重視的節日Songkran（潑水節）今年受到疫情影響，但Davika卻未有破壞過節心情，連日來在IG分享靚相滿足fans，並刺激其IG的追隨人數衝破1300萬大關，為答謝網民支持，她特別分享在沙灘拍攝的性感寫真，獲網民大讚似足美人魚。<br />\n<br />\nDavika既是當紅花旦亦是影后，曾主演泰國賣座電影《嚇鬼阿嫂》（Pee Mak），近排則有新劇《婉通夫人》於當地播出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZQIGgI5L6GjGm7XLx5W6HKg_ZVM=/802x717/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/72HQZAIAHZHPBCAOEZ6O7MURFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZQIGgI5L6GjGm7XLx5W6HKg_ZVM%3D%2F802x717%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F72HQZAIAHZHPBCAOEZ6O7MURFM.jpg&h=b7bfa98f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/LSLFxcK98z4G1YXO_BrOitNDTS4=/802x1003/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/B2E5UPEG75DLNLOHPYSS2WE5GA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FLSLFxcK98z